com.complexible.common.io
Interface Page

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractPage
public interface Page

A Page represents a collection of bytes that can be written/read. Usually corresponds to a fixed-size section from a PagedFile.

Since:
0.3
Version:
2.1
Author:
Pedro Oliveira, Michael Grove
